{"tid":1487643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作為攬炒派，入一入嚟投票定一定軍心。","createTime":"2019-08-19T10:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T13:40:19.000Z","uid":167548,"like":206,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e06ac7f02d5a2bff4a74c13a71568677eb479c5b","tid":1487643,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n收皮啦P牌東區友, 口講攬炒, 最尾一刻賣隊友。比老鼠成大兩大就驚撚左。同中共談判你憑咩代表我。我地只接受全面落實5大訴求, 或者拉埋中共一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">ALL or Nothing <br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d111d1b5ffc0a4fba3290e12f8e6e4ccbb88bc3e","tid":1487643,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"你一怯就沒左成個香港, 你對唔對得住6位殉道者同埋700位手足。<br />\nDLLMCFHON79"},{"pid":"e987526aae004b223e4b001ed5a6aa4072972a50","tid":1487643,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />p 無得投"},{"pid":"80a5d97af54d8e499d26bc52dc5630c7046b7372","tid":1487643,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"條P牌友所有假設, 中共玩完, 世界各國唔會踩多幾腳, 香港一樣會重生。<br />\n我地寧願攬炒都唔要下一代繼續活是中共控制下"},{"pid":"3cad96fcd0533e6ec45ca86e6ac80951d6d4f890","tid":1487643,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"攬炒唔是談判手段！是事在必行！你覺得老共會讓步想錯你個心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b501cf4117c97e3b12e433129970634f7906e28","tid":1487643,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cad96fcd0533e6ec45ca86e6ac80951d6d